profile_summary:
Muhammed Rishad s r is a driven and accomplished developer with a solid foundation in JavaScript, HTML, and CSS. As a forward-thinking IT student at CUSAT and founder of the innovative EdTech startup NoTime, Muhammed brings a unique blend of technical expertise and entrepreneurial insight to his work, focusing on cutting-edge MERN stack development and cloud platforms.

With an impressive portfolio of 82 public repositories, Muhammed has established himself as a prolific and creative developer, committed to delivering high-quality solutions that meet the evolving needs of the digital landscape. As a leader in his field, Muhammed is followed by a growing network of 27 professionals, a testament to his influence and dedication to innovation in the tech community.
